OL,3,CChildren in England waiting years for
OL,4,Cautism and cerebral palsy diagnoses
OL,6,FYears-long waits for diagnoses and
OL,7,Fsupport for autistic young people in
OL,8,FEngland and others with conditions
OL,9,Fincluding cerebral palsy is "robbing"
OL,10,Fthem of their childhoods, the
OL,11,FChildren's Commissioner has warned.
OL,13,FChildren with cerebral palsy faced the
OL,14,Fhighest wait of all for diagnosis
OL,15,Fthrough community health services, at
OL,16,Fthree years and four months on
OL,17,Faverage, according to data obtained by
OL,18,FDame Rachel de Souza's office.
