OL,3,CChildren in England waiting years for
OL,4,Cautism and cerebral palsy diagnoses
OL,6,FDame Rachel has used her legislative
OL,7,Fpowers to access previously
OL,8,Funpublished data from NHS England to
OL,9,Fshow a "joined-up national picture of
OL,10,Fchildren's waiting times" for the two
OL,11,Fyears to March 2024.
OL,13,FWaiting lists are long through both
OL,14,Froutes, Dame Rachel said but added
OL,15,Fthat times for the first contact with
OL,16,Fcommunity services appeared higher.
