OL,3,CChildren in England waiting years for
OL,4,Cautism and cerebral palsy diagnoses
OL,6,FThe data revealed that almost a
OL,7,Fquarter (23%) of children diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith attention deficit hyperactivity
OL,9,Fdisorder (ADHD) waited more than four
OL,10,Fyears after their referral for a
OL,11,Fdiagnosis in community health services.
OL,13,FAlmost one in six (15%) waited more
OL,14,Fthan four years for their diagnosis of
OL,15,Fautism through this route, the
OL,16,Fcommissioner's office said.
