OL,3,CChildren in England waiting years for
OL,4,Cautism and cerebral palsy diagnoses
OL,6,FOverall, the research showed that
OL,7,F400,000 children in England were still
OL,8,Fwaiting at the end of March 2023 to
OL,9,Fget a first appointment after being
OL,10,Freferred to community services or
OL,11,Fchildren's mental health services,
OL,12,Fwhich the commissioner said was
OL,13,Fequivalent to around 3% of the
OL,14,Fnation's total child population.
