OL,3,CChildren in England waiting years for
OL,4,Cautism and cerebral palsy diagnoses
OL,6,FDame Rachel said: "These findings are
OL,7,Fa stark reminder of the daily fight
OL,8,Fchildren and their families face
OL,9,Fseeking support for neurodevelopmental
OL,10,Fconditions like autism and ADHD, and
OL,11,Fhow the system has failed to keep pace
OL,12,Fwith rising demand.
OL,14,F"These children face an invisible
OL,15,Fcrisis, in a system that is working
OL,16,Fagainst itself by forcing families to
OL,17,Fjump through multiple hoops in a
OL,18,Fcomplex and lengthy process of
OL,19,Fassessment, diagnosis and
OL,20,Fintervention."
