OL,6,F"We know patients are still waiting
OL,7,Ftoo long for an ADHD diagnosis and
OL,8,Fthat's why the NHS has launched an
OL,9,Findependent expert taskforce to
OL,10,Finvestigate the challenges facing
OL,11,Fservices, help them manage the rising
OL,12,Fnumbers of referrals, and continue to
OL,13,Ftransform care to ensure everyone gets
OL,14,Fthe support they need."
OL,16,FA government spokesperson said: "For
OL,17,Ftoo long children and young people
OL,18,Fwith autism, ADHD and other
OL,19,Fneurological conditions have been let
OL,20,Fdown by a broken NHS.
